org.uncommons.watchmaker.framework
Class PopulationData<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.uncommons.watchmaker.framework.PopulationData<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of evolved entity present in the population that this data describes.
public final class PopulationData<T>
extends Object

Immutable data object containing statistics about the state of an evolved population and a reference to the fittest candidate solution in the population.

Author:
Daniel Dyer
See Also:
EvolutionObserver
